# Ledgerium AI — Process Intelligence Layer

## Purpose

This document defines the Process Intelligence Layer (PIL), the system responsible for transforming individual workflow executions into aggregated insights, performance metrics, and actionable process intelligence.

It enables Ledgerium AI to move from:
- capturing workflows
→ to understanding, comparing, and optimizing them

---

## Scope

This document covers:
- aggregation of ProcessRuns
- process comparison and normalization
- metrics generation
- variant detection
- process performance analysis
- drift detection

This document does NOT cover:
- event capture (recorder)
- deterministic workflow reconstruction (DPE)
- UI visualization details

---

